OL,5, Former chancellor Nadhim Zahawi has    
OL,6, made a surprise appearance in an ITV   
OL,7, drama about the Post Office IT scandal.
OL,9,FHe plays himself questioning then-Post 
OL,10,FOffice chief executive Paula Vennells  
OL,11,Fin a 2015 Commons committee inquiry    
OL,12,Finto the Horizon computer system.      
OL,14,FThe drama is being screened this week. 
OL,16,FBetween 1999 and 2015, more than 700   
OL,17,Fsub-postmasters and sub-postmistresses 
OL,18,Fwere wrongly prosecuted for false      
OL,19,Faccounting, theft and fraud, on the    
OL,20,Fbasis of faulty Horizon information.   
